        {
            "title": "花旗在等待日本買家重回債市 相信在那之後日圓仍有大幅上漲空間",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日圓自2024年8月份以來最強勁的三日漲勢，仍不足以讓花旗集團策略師Daniel Tobon轉為看漲日圓。他表示，要讓漲勢延續，日本買家需要再次開始把資金轉回國內債券市場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「最大的交易機會在於等待那個轉折點，等待我們看到拐點的那一刻，」他在一次採訪中說。「一旦你看到了那種確認信號，在那之後日圓可能還有超過15%的上漲空間。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/plDtKFz7476hStmQMTVK1g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a2a202355c5131fac8b7a680d0583672\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近期的漲勢源於市場猜測日本和美國正準備出手支撐日圓。此前日圓一度跌至接近1美元兌160日圓，接近促使日本官員在2024年干預市場的水平。日圓周二又上漲1%，升至1美元兌153日圓下方。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c090829c-ecdb-3f24-aa0a-584cb09e3788-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日圓突然反轉發生在日本債券市場上周遭遇沉重拋售之後，當時投資者擔憂首相高市早苗的財政計畫將加重政府本已沉重的債務負擔。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這輪暴跌推動日本國債殖利率大幅上升，可能促使投資者將資金從海外撤回並在國內重新投資。這也提高了對沖基金平倉套息交易的可能性，也就是以日本的低利率借入資金，再把資金投向利率更高的國家。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Tobon表示，他仍然認為在下個月選舉臨近之際，日圓存在再次走弱的風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「如果我看到本土資金開始轉向買入日本國債，那將是更強的信號，表明現在是買入日圓的時候，因為這會開始緩解財政方面的擔憂，」他說。「這可能在選舉之後很快發生，也可能要更久以後才會出現。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Citi Sees Bigger Yen Rally Hanging on Shift Back to Japan Bonds</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8A%B1%E6%97%97%E5%9C%A8%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E9%87%8D%E5%9B%9E%E5%82%B5%E5%B8%82-%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E5%9C%A8%E9%82%A3%E4%B9%8B%E5%BE%8C%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93-201504568.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 05:34:26",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "SQM稱天齊鋰業上訴被駁回 與Codelco合資項目獲放行",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 智利最高法院駁回<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:天齊鋰業;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/天齊鋰業\">天齊鋰業</a>針對鋰生產商智利化工礦業公司(SQM)與智利金屬巨頭智利國家銅業公司(Codelco)合資企業提出的上訴，為這一可能打造電池市場關鍵鋰生產商的協議掃清了障礙。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SQM在周二提交的文件中表示，公司已於1月26日獲悉最高法院的裁決。該裁決維持了聖地亞哥上訴法院此前駁回天齊鋰業訴訟請求的裁決。天齊鋰業曾於去年11月向智利最高法院提起上訴。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SQM表示：「因此，合併所附帶的解除條件被認定未被觸發，從而在所有法律層面鞏固了其完成。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3c5c279a-98fe-3cba-97bc-d2e3c624b7df-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這個名為NovaAndino Litio的合營公司旨在憑借低成本和不斷成長的需求打造全球最大的電池用鋰生產商。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題SQM Says Codelco Venture Greenlit After Tianqi Appeal Rejection</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Carolina Pulice.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sqm%E7%A8%B1%E5%A4%A9%E9%BD%8A%E9%8B%B0%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E8%A2%AB%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E-%E8%88%87codelco%E5%90%88%E8%B3%87%E9%A0%85%E7%9B%AE%E7%8D%B2%E6%94%BE%E8%A1%8C-223129031.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 07:33:04",
