        {
            "title": "LVMH第四季度時裝和皮具業務銷售疲軟 表明奢侈品公司繼續承壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Nathan Laine/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sMM0oxvPjkVqe9PzA369nQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/acabc1c7ae87c45f4b780d689cb1a912\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Nathan Laine/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> LVMH旗下關鍵的時裝業務的銷售在假日季出現下滑，表明這家路易威登的母公司仍在承受需求疲軟帶來的壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">LVMH周二在聲明中表示，時裝與皮具部門第四季度有機銷售額下降3%。分析師此前預計降幅為2.94%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聲明發布後，LVMH在紐約交易的美國存託憑證下跌1%。執行長Bernard Arnault表示，集團面臨艱難的經營環境，並警告2026年不太可能一帆風順。他對投資者稱，LVMH因此將在今年限制開支。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-07065c24-2104-3c76-b792-91b0ec88b9d6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於生活成本壓力與地緣政治不確定性正在拖累支出，奢侈品公司一直難以從緊隨疫情後繁榮期的低迷中反彈。此外，大幅提價也引發了消費者的強烈不滿。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"巴黎路易威登奢侈品店櫥窗裡的待售商品。攝影：Nathan Laine/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YB8Xnvp.pYB7yIebk4VuNA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6d02afb6d5e4def633c0fea9f898ec11\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">巴黎路易威登奢侈品店櫥窗裡的待售商品。攝影：Nathan Laine/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行業中也有一些公司表現更具韌性，比如卡地亞的所有者歷峰集團。在形勢不明朗的時期，消費者認為金項鏈、手鏈等比時髦手袋更能保值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管LVMH在腕表與珠寶領域的佈局較小，但該業務在最新季度的表現好於預期，幫助公司在時裝與皮具疲弱的情況下，整體銷售仍勉強實現小幅成長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第四季度，美國以及包含中國的地區有機銷售額均成長1%，高於分析師預估。歐洲下降2%和日本下降5%的降幅都大於預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">LVMH表示，全年經常性經營利潤為178億歐元，同比下降9.3%，但好於分析師預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題LVMH Suffers Sluggish Sales of High-End Fashion and Handbags (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/lvmh%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E6%99%82%E8%A3%9D%E5%92%8C%E7%9A%AE%E5%85%B7%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E7%96%B2%E8%BB%9F-%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E5%A5%A2%E4%BE%88%E5%93%81%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E6%89%BF%E5%A3%93-193345308.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 05:27:58",
